<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīmatu mahāmaṁḍalīsvara 
<lb n="2"/>kannaradēvaṁḍu mūḍu <unclear>pu</unclear> 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṭla nēla mrindikaṁṭi mallikā 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>rjjanadēvaraku yiccina nēla 
<lb n="5"/>rudrapaṁḍitulakunu 
<lb n="6"/>vritti dīni jeḍaka rakṣiṁci 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>na gaṁgakartta vēvurubrāhmanu 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>lakunu vēvuru tapō<unclear>ja</unclear>nulaku 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nu veṭṭina phalamu dīnini Evva 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>rēni tappikonna gaṁgakartta vē 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>yi kavilala jaṁpina pāpa 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>muna paḍuduru <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> bōli 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>nāyakuṁḍunuṁ tō<unclear>ḍu</unclear> 
<lb n="14"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="7" unit="character"/> 
</p>

